column2: Setup of ECOLodge Scattering Pit experiment "Boptics". ASD measurements over both 'clean' (A) and 'disturbed' (B) area prior to snow work and clearing. Measured from each corner starting from Stbd-stern corner (1) in clockwise direction. Amy did NIR/ small snow pit/microCT in each A+B. ASD measurements again of both after shoveling/clearing.
